        <p class="rutas-hero-subtitle" id="canon-intl-subtitle">If 421 were a library, these would be the 25 books that never leave the shelf. The texts that best represent what we do, why we do it, and how we do it.</p>
      </div>
      <hr class="rutas-gradient-divider">

      <!-- Canon container: JS will populate this -->
